!!!! Getting to the confrence place

Villeneuve d'Ascq is a city at 15-20 min of metro from Lille center (downtown). *Ilévia>https://www.ilevia.fr/* is the public transport operator for the Lille Métropole. There are metro every couple of minutes in rush hours. Take the metro Line 1 (Yellow) in the direction of "4 Cantons Stade" and stop at "4 Cantons" (terminus). From there you can walk to Building B of the Inria or take Bus 66 (Direction "Eglise (Forest-sur-Marque)") or 72 (direction "Maison D'accueil (Baisieux)") to the "Halley" stop (second stop) which has a frequency between 15 to 20 minutes. || {{{ <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m26!1m12!1m3!1d1266.083627908925!2d3.1457262033925493!3d50.605429561389855!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!4m11!3e2!4m5!1s0x47c2d6521109b35b%3A0x283f2c5d6883466c!2s4%20Cantons%20Stade%2C%20Villeneuve-d&#39;Ascq!3m2!1d50.605239999999995!2d3.139122!4m3!3m2!1d50.605077699999995!2d3.1488592!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sfr!4v1709133165893!5m2!1ses!2sfr" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe> }}}

